Functional Requirements
FR1: System shall allow student identification via NFC card
FR2: System shall record attendance automatically
FR3: System shall prevent duplicate attendance entries
FR4: System shall allow lecturers to view attendance reports
FR5: System shall allow administrators to manage users
FR6: System shall store attendance history
FR7: System shall generate attendance reports

Non-Functional Requirements
Security: Only authenticated users can access system
Performance: Attendance must be recorded within 2 seconds
Reliability: System must operate during lecture hours without failure
Usability: Interface must be simple and user-friendly
Scalability: System must support multiple faculties
